rain; Louisville 71 foggy; Memphis 75 cloudy; Nashville 73 cloudy;
New Orleans 80 fair; North Platte 55 fair; Oklahoma City 73
thunderstorms; Omaha 62 fair; Rapid City 58 fair; St. Louis 70 fair;
